<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <title>アルバイト履歴書</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        table.main, div.main {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1320px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border: none;
        }

        div.main > div {
            float: left;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 10px;
            line-height: 20px;
        }

        td, th {
            border: 1px solid #000; /* Combined the border properties */
            padding: 8px;
            vertical-align: top;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .border-right-unset {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .border-left-unset {
            border-left: none; /* Removed !important for CSS2 compatibility */
        }

        .main__block-head {
            border: none; /* This applies to the block itself */
        }

        .main__block-head__cv-title {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0; /* Changed 'none' to '0' */
        }

        .main__block-head__date {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .main__block-head__date__title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .main__block-head__date__date {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .main__block-second__col-title {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .main__block-second__col-title__title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .main__block-second__col-title__sub-title {
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .main__block-second__col-text {
            border-left: none;
        }

        .main__block-second__col-img {
            border-top: none;
            border-right: none;
        }

        .main__block-head > td {
            border: none;
        }

        /* Widths for colspan */
        td[colspan="1"] {
            width: 7.69%;
        }

        td[colspan="2"] {
            width: 15.38%;
        }

        td[colspan="3"] {
            width: 23.08%;
        }

        td[colspan="4"] {
            width: 30.77%;
        }

        td[colspan="5"] {
            width: 38.46%;
        }

        td[colspan="6"] {
            width: 46.15%;
        }

        td[colspan="7"] {
            width: 53.85%;
        }

        td[colspan="8"] {
            width: 61.54%;
        }

        td[colspan="9"] {
            width: 69.23%;
        }

        td[colspan="10"] {
            width: 76.92%;
        }

        td[colspan="11"] {
            width: 84.61%;
        }

        td[colspan="12"] {
            width: 92.31%;
        }

        td[colspan="13"] {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .font-15 {
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .font-10 {
            font-size: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<table style="margin-bottom: 30px" class="main">
    <tr class="main__block-head">
        <td colspan="6" class="main__block-head__cv-title">
            <div>
                アルバイト履 歴 書
            </div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="4" class="main__block-head__date">
            <div class="main__block-head__date__title">
                年 月 日　現在
            </div>
            <div class="main__block-head__date__date">
                yyyy/mm/dd as of now
            </div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3">
            <img style="width: 100%" src="../image/image-2025-06-04-15-46-00-326.png" alt="">
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title"
            style="border-bottom: 1px dashed #000 !important;background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">フリガナ</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Furigana</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="8" class="main__block-second__col-text" style="border-bottom: 1px dashed #000 !important;">
        </td>
        <td colspan="2" rowspan="4" class="main__block-second__col-img">
            写真 ID Photo (30mm×40mm)
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title"
            style="border-top: 1px dashed #000 !important;background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">名 前</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Name</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="8" class="main__block-second__col-text" style="border-top: 1px dashed #000 !important;">
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">国 籍</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Nationality</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="8" class="main__block-second__col-text">
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">生年月日</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Date of birth</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="8" class="main__block-second__col-text">
            Date of birth 年 月 日 (満 歳)
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">住 所</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Address</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="5" class="main__block-second__col-text border-right-unset">
        </td>
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title border-left-unset" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">近くの駅</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Nearest Station</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3" class="main__block-second__col-text"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">電話番号</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Tel</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3" class="main__block-second__col-text border-right-unset">
        </td>
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title border-left-unset" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">E-mail</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="6" class="main__block-second__col-text"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">在留資格</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Status of residence</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="4" class="main__block-second__col-text border-right-unset">
        </td>
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title border-left-unset" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">在留期限</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Period of stay</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="4" class="main__block-second__col-text">
            <div>年 月 日 まで有効</div>
            <div>*Valid until yyyy/mm/dd</div>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="main__block-second">
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">学校名</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">School name</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="5" class="main__block-second__col-text border-right-unset">
        </td>
        <td colspan="2" class="main__block-second__col-title border-left-unset" style="background: #e9ecef;">
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__title">近くの駅</div>
            <div class="main__block-second__col-title__sub-title">Nearest</div>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3" class="main__block-second__col-text">
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<table class="main">
    <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center; background-color: #e9ecef;">
            <span class="font-15"
                  style="margin-right: 20px; font-weight: 600">母国・日本での　学歴 ／ 職歴 ／ 受賞歴 </span>
            <span class="font-10">Education history / Employment history / Awards received (in your home country &amp; in Japan)</span>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="height: 400px;"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center; background-color: #e9ecef;">
            <span class="font-15" style="margin-right: 20px; font-weight: 600">資格 ／ 免許 </span>
            <span class="font-10">Qualifications / Licenses</span>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="height: 100px;"></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<div class="main">
    <div style="width: 5%">注意</div>
    <div style="width: 50%">
        <div>1.黒いボールペンで書く</div>
        <div>2.全て日本語で書く（外国の学校名などはカタカナまたは英語で書く）</div>
        <div>3.※マークがついているところは◯をつける</div>
    </div>
    <div style="width: 45%">
        <div>1.Please write with a black ballpen.</div>
        <div>2.Please write everything in Japanese.<br>
            (Names of schools may be written either in katakana or English)
        </div>
        <div>3.Please circle the applicable option for section with ※</div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
